Try something like this:

``` js
const old = __webpack_get_script_filename__;
const queryMap = new Map();
__webpack_get_script_filename__ = (chunkId) => {
  const filename = old(chunkId);
  return filename + (queryMap.get(chunkId) || "");
};

const old2 = __webpack_chunk_load__;
__webpack_chunk_load__ = (chunkId) => {
  const result = old2(chunkId);
  return result.catch(err => {
    queryMap.set(chunkId, "?" + Math.random());
    // you may add automatic retry here
    throw err;
  });
}
```

Note that query should be constant when no error occurs to not break prefetching, etc. which also use the filename

